data.description: Cottage-like home in the heart of Hill Country! 3 bed/3.5 bath two story home + 1 bed/1 bath Guest Suite in sought-after Cypress Rapids neighborhood. Nestled on just over a half acre cul de sac lot with mature shade trees. Light and bright living room upon entry with minimalist fireplace, built-in storage, and cathedral ceiling. Kitchen offers built-in SS appliances, brilliant white cabinetry and complimentary light-toned counters with large center island, and breakfast bar. Enjoy sharing a meal in the formal dining room with access to the backyard or breakfast nook. Primary bedroom features cozy fireplace, bay window ideal for seating area, double vanity, oversized walk-in tile shower, and garden tub. First Floor complete remodel done in 2020. Gameroom with access to exterior deck + generously sized secondary bedrooms and bathrooms upstairs. Private Guest Suite located above the three car detached garage. Relax under shade of the covered patio or enjoy your favorite outdoor activities in your private backyard. Relax and enjoy a short golf cart ride to downtown Gruene for live music, dinner, dancing or shopping, and tubing in the sparkling Guadalupe River.
